    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, a definitive icon of the Golden Era. This example features the highly sought-after 13B-REW twin-rotor engine, with the sequential turbocharging system operating with factory-spec efficiency. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp five-speed manual gearbox and a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring balanced power delivery. The aluminum double-wishbone suspension remains tight, providing the telepathic handling these Series 6 models are renowned for. This vehicle has been kept in a climate-controlled environment, preserving the integrity of the complex vacuum line network and ensuring the apex seals remain in peak condition. With zero modifications and a flawless exterior, this is a turnkey investment for the discerning collector seeking mechanical purity.",
